BUILD:
  - make sure SNX_BASE_DIR is set to where sonix is installed.
    typically I do this:
      setenv SNX_BASE_DIR /usr/share/sonix-installed/
      setenv LD_LIBRARY_PATH /usr/lib:/usr/local/lib:"$SNX_BASE_DIR"/lib

  - you'll need opengl and glut.
  - type make
  
